The right side `RelIO.liftFinf n (λ i => g (f i))` is an `AssocList Nat β` constructed by taking `fin_range n`, mapping `λ i => g (f i)` over it, and converting to `AssocList`. So, the pairs would be `⟨↑(i.toNat), g (f i)⟩` for each `i` in `fin_range n`.

